, peace\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41207,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/20\/missing-salat-al-asr\/","url_meta":{"origin":28533,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salah: Warning against missing congregational \u2018Asr prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 20, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever misses the afternoon prayer, it is as if he had lost his family and his property.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 552, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 626 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15928,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/09\/05\/masjid-prayer-twenty-seven-better\/","url_meta":{"origin":28533,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Jama&#8217;ah: Prayer in mosque is twenty seven times better","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 5, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPrayer in congregation is better than prayer alone by twenty-seven degrees.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 645, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 650 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim Ibn Qudamah said, \"Congregational prayer is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26120,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/03\/26\/door-masajid-women\/","url_meta":{"origin":28533,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Mosques: The Prophet makes women&#8217;s door in Masjid","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 26, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIt would be better if you had left this door to the mosque for women.\u201d Nafi\u2019 said, \u201cIbn Umar never again entered through it until the day he died.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 462 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13527,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/11\/virtue-fajr-jamaah-jumuah\/","url_meta":{"origin":28533,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Fajr: Dawn prayer in congregation on Friday","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 11, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the best of prayers to Allah is the dawn prayer in congregation on Friday.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n 2790 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u064e \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u0